data.description: Amazing location and great investment opportunity to own two detached shore homes just steps away from the beach in Manasquan! Consistent rental history this property can be perfect for a summer/winter rental investment, owner occupant with rental income, or rare opportunity to build your dream home at the Jersey Shore. This property backs up to Fishermans Cove, the last undeveloped & protected tract on the Manasquan Inlet. This family friendly 55-acre site offers fishing, sunbathing and is considered one of the best dog friendly beaches at the shore. This is a private oasis that will feature protected views for your new dream home for years to come, no risk for any development behind you and losing views of the pristine natural coastal habitat.Both units will be delivered furnished.
